{"tid":1846962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國防部證實有軍機在阿富汗墜毀　否認被擊落","createTime":"2020-01-27T21:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T02:59:08.000Z","uid":125193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"acda317f138e7be1b565e9f67f96dec0be6e789f","tid":1846962,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:05:43.000Z","msg":"美國國防部證實，一架軍方飛機昨日在阿富汗加茲尼省墜毀，但否認是被阿富汗塔利班武裝份子擊落。軍方發言人在聲明中，未有交代墜機原因，正調查事故，強調沒有跡象表明飛機是遭到敵對勢力擊落。從網上片段看到飛機殘骸部分已經燒到變黑，機艙內仍然有火光。<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒引述一名美國空軍表示，機上約有數人，據報墜毀的是美軍的龐巴迪E-11A電子偵察機。<br />\n<br />\n阿富汗塔利班聲稱是他們的武裝分子將飛機擊落，發言人穆賈希德表示，這架飛機當時正執行情報任務，在加茲尼省達耶地區被擊落，機上乘客包括有美軍高層，但聲明沒有提及組織使用什麼武器。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505177-20200128.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505177-20200128.htm&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5re6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=9d6cc8b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505177-20200128.htm&h=33c8d8d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505177-20200128.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7cea3586e33ff147d4cccaf368b5e06751b80eda","tid":1846962,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4eed2a89cee6cb9f3276df613ad908c32ded31","tid":1846962,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d8aee0e390bd99bdb141b955e12f198cc3754c","tid":1846962,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:19:51.000Z","msg":"-O-O"},{"pid":"cf6e88441ff1045786e5f741915f1be1843f9b28","tid":1846962,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T22:05:56.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦"},{"pid":"bd205376d5